title: My Love From Another Star Season 1 Complete
description:
Do Min Joon is otherworldly, literally. Since being marooned on Earth for 400 years, Min Joon has diligently observed humans for centuries, ultimately coming to cynical conclusions, re-inventing himself every decade or so and staying under the radar. On top of being stunningly handsome, Min Joon has enhanced vision, hearing, agility and other powers Ã¢â‚¬â€ all the more reason to believe he's superior to everyone on Earth. That is, until he pursues the beautiful but spoiled, petulant and arrogant actress Cheon Song Yi for a romance that is out of this world and seemingly spans time. 

21 episodes. Approximately 59 minutes each.
